{"tid":2231625,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【中二病】唔想造神 但係攬炒巴個名令我諗起一個東晉復國名將","createTime":"2020-10-05T19:44:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-06T01:55:43.000Z","uid":154486,"like":39,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"212e62f2a5ca4f98480383bf5c0b0a456903181a","tid":2231625,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T19:44:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ndorz1Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNdorz1Q.jpg&h=acf38cb2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>祖逖</strong></span><br />\n（粵拼：zou2&nbsp;tik1；266年&mdash;321年10月[1]），字士稚，係東晉將領，范陽郡逎縣（而家河北保定淶水）人，喺北伐期間收復過黃河南面嘅大幅領土。<br />\n<br />\n東晉時期祖逖多次北伐，要光復故土，雖然最尾功敗垂成，但係佢既事蹟好多都係關於堅持同唔好放棄：<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\">聞雞起舞</span></strong><br />\n《晉書．祖逖傳》：「與司空劉琨均為司州主簿，情好綢繆，共被同寢。中夜聞荒雞鳴，蹴琨覺曰︰『此非惡聲也。』因起舞。」<br />\n<br />\n聽見雞鳴就起身，比喻人發奮學習，勵精圖治。<br />\n聽到雞叫就起來舞劍。後比喻有志報國的人及時奮起。<br />\n比喻有志之士及時奮發自勵，自我鞭策。<br />\n聞：聽到。起：起床。舞：舞劍。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><strong>中流擊楫</strong></span><br />\n晉朝祖逖率軍北伐，渡江至中流時，擊打船槳而立誓恢復中原。<br />\n典出《晉書．卷六二．祖逖傳》。比喻收復失土，報效國家的壯烈情懷。《五代史平話．梁史．卷上》：「晉罹五胡之亂，而祖逖擊楫中流，誓在興復。」<br />\n<br />\n話我迷信打飛機又好，而家世界各地好撚多個香港人敢開名企出黎幫手，好值得我地尊敬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n無論身在何方，真正既香港人都以光復故土作為終生目標<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6924ae8c1e0ec3a5503ee2fde621d5dfa549e9c","tid":2231625,"uid":204466,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T19:45:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a79c59e2333efe1458c73f8b7f08548ac2749955","tid":2231625,"uid":348825,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T19:46:28.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb497b31e0620013855fe840e64ffcec4577cf68","tid":2231625,"uid":154486,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T19:49:05.000Z","msg":"成地精又如何<br />\n人地做左咁多野，如果唔係攬炒團隊第一個打開國際線，我地可能唔會行到呢一步"},{"pid":"7b6b4a6c5f7d78093dff5d86ccff24f84012ae5a","tid":2231625,"uid":263150,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"bb497b31e0620013855fe840e64ffcec4577cf68","tid":2231625,"uid":154486,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T19:49:05.000Z","msg":"成地精又如何<br />\n人地做左咁多野，如果唔係攬炒團隊第一個打開國際線，我地可能唔會行到呢一步"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T20:19:47.000Z","msg":"攬炒團隊真係行得好前 ！"},{"pid":"f92ed464383663068816652683ede254f7021824","tid":2231625,"uid":171107,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T20:27:00.000Z","msg":"造神有咩問題，求神拜佛佢將來唔好變質，或被屈變質<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bed09cb01364e1ed8d454fa56d4e84cc49dd6b56","tid":2231625,"uid":28759,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T21:22:28.000Z","msg":"造神不如助神 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc1508dce7e81deb053bbc44b9fe1ccb83825904","tid":2231625,"uid":276273,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T01:28:20.000Z","msg":"咁 lunch 哥又有邊會神人相似？"},{"pid":"6530f5ada8cadd1209ebcd603465ba9e9bc9a89b","tid":2231625,"uid":34140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T01:42:29.000Z","msg":"佢出真身都係為左保命啫<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9298852572f63381f29b673e44a7e8b7edc617ac","tid":2231625,"uid":14918,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T01:50:01.000Z","msg":"支那好似東晉後16國 , 各個民族獨立建國先係正路"},{"pid":"e95cf2384c9d6c1dbd0e6c71851db41d5f2e9c2d","tid":2231625,"uid":8257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f92ed464383663068816652683ede254f7021824","tid":2231625,"uid":171107,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"